i havent updated in forever. i have been so busy with band. blah. so far we have won grand champions at both contests. we are going to a contest this weekend at greenbrier. im so excited. i hope we win. it would be nice to win every competition so we can make fun of the football team and say that we won everything. i g2g finish my homework.

wow. i am soo tired i just got home from band camp which was fun except for the whole marching part. i am so sore and i want to go to bed. christi our flag coach is not coming back unless she gets like $300. it was sooo sad i am going to miss her soo much. everybody cried. im sorta glad band camp is over because of all the drama it was pretty much like school cause pretty much everybody cried. it was probably better than last years but we didnt get to have a shaving cream fight and the seniors didnt get to trash the field. but we had fun in our cabin playing pranks on each other.im going to go to bed and get some sleep so see ya later.

im soooo sry that i havent updated in like forever. ive been soo busy this summer it is not even funny. i went to busch gardens, went to kings island twice, went to the wave pool a couple of times, been at flag practice and band camp, and spending time with my friends. and now i am leaving to go to band camp in 30 minutes. im soooo excited it is going to be so much fun. i got to go finish packing for camp see ya later.

sry i havent updated in awile. first of all ive moved into a new house(near cyndi and brittaney). i am now dating jd(which i am having second thoughts about). i am soo excited that school is almost out so i dont have to deal with the drama anymore.

1. Why have we drifted apart? i dont no really, i guess you got popular and i just stayed the same
2. How do you like flag? flag is really fun! i like it a whole lot better than marching
3. Do you like Mrs.Preston...? not really. she is really strict and gives stupid assignments. besides that i like her sumtimes.
4. WHY WON'T YOU GET A BOYFRIEND?!?!?! jd has asked me out but im not sure if i can trust him so i said i might be doing sumething this weekend
5. Will you teach me to twirl? yes i will. just tell me when u want me to come over.

im still sick but i feel a whole better. ill probably go to school tomorrow if i feel like it. i found out that i have a relly bad sinus infection and it is not contagios.*(however u spell it) i just dont like being sick. it sucks really bad.i also miss all of my friends.
i hate being sick it feels bad. i left school because i almost past out. im also excited cause in a few weeks im moving near cyndi and rachel.

thank u ali and stephanie for doing this layout for me. it is like the best thing ever. im so excited, there is only 30 school days left!!!!!(not counting weekends and day offs)oh and there is 8 months until christmas. our vacation bible school is like the coolest thing ever!!!! it is construction stuff and it is so cute.and there is a teenagers group. and since there is a new church taking our building we are going to have more kids. oh and the weekend before we r having a carnival!!!!!(thanx to the new church)and in the summer we r having a lock in at jennifers. and in september we r going to columbus for a girls teenager thingy.(5 tickets left) so if u wanna come just talk to me.

i had a good day today. first of all every band at spring valley got ones or superior ratings. then we went to the mall and i found out that rachel henson is not mean and she is not going to beat me up. she is actually really nice. i found out that jd is a huge liar and he is getting on my nerves.i also have a friend with me on mallets.(demi-thanx for doing that)and today is the start of spring break. i just had a good day today.

life sucks. ive been put in band two with no friends in the flute section,(no offense to Lee and Kayleen)and everyone else thinks i should be in the top band. all they did was put all of the people that was in front of me in all county band and put them in top band. the only friend i wiil have in there wiil be rachel and she plays mallets. hopefully they will put stephanie stroud in second band. i also wont be in the band with the person i like.

I love 4 day weekends. i wish they were always 4 days. Our competion Saturday was awesome. We won first place on everything, even our dance one 'caus this one girl fell down twice. So i didnt think we were going to win.
